data.description: Beautiful spacious home that needs nothing! Freshly painted and with new floors upstairs, just move in! All appliances stay! From the moment you step inside, this home features high ceilings, lots of natural light, an an excellent flowing floor plan. All bedrooms are upstairs and you'll be impressed by the master suite!! Home backs up to a neighborhood pond with fountain. Living room pre-wired for surround sound. Irrigation system. No CDD fees/low HOA fees. Assigned to Wildlight Elementary!
